    "causal_summary": "Phase C of 114 follow-on roadmap. Ship two related improvements to cli-devin SWE-1.6 dispatches: (1) per-model token-budget engine adapted from smallcode-master src/context/budget.ms — token allocation defaults, fit-to-budget truncation with `[... N tokens cut]` markers, priority eviction; (2) output-verification pipeline adapted from smallcode src/governor/verifier.ms + hard_fail.ms — compile→execute→smoke-test→lint with confidence scoring, refuse-to-ship gate on hard-fail. Effort: ~28 hours across 3 internal sub-packets. Daily quality lift on the most-used dispatch surface.",
